Modify the Battle Station Page Layout
Setup --> Object Manager --> Battle Station --> Page Layouts --> Battle Station Layout --> Battle Station Detail section --> drag the Project Status field to the right column (below Owner field).
--> Drag the Weapons Status field to the right column (below Project Status field).
===================================================================================================================================================================================================================
Resources (Click the wrench icon) --> Add --> Quantity and Utilization field to the right side by selecting them --> OK
Supplies (Click the wrench icon) --> Add --> Quantity, Unit Cost, and Total Cost field to the right side by selecting them --> OK --> Save
===================================================================================================================================================================================================================
Add Some Battle Station Data
App Luncher --> Battle Station Construction --> Battle Stations --> New --> Battle Station Name: Obliteration Station --> Save

