Add a Roll-Up Summary Field
Setup --> Object Manager --> Battle Station --> Fields & Relationships --> New --> Data Type: Roll-Up Summary --> Next -->
Field Label: Crew Members
Field Name: Crew_Members --> Next -->
Summarized Object : Resources 
Select Roll-Up Type : SUM
Field to Aggregate : Quantity --> Next --> Next --> Save
